      "raw_text": "(By United Press Leased Wire)\n\n\nPORTLAND, July 26.-What la\nDor leaders declare to be the first\nstep in a deliberate effort to break\nfthe power the labor unions In\nPortland was taken by members OF\nthe retail association last night\nwhen it was decided that the as,\nISOLATION would stand for an open\nshop\"\n\n\nThirty-three out of the AZ mem\nbers of the organization were pres\nent They unanimously endorsed\nq resolution which follows:\n\n\n1--WE stand for the open shop,\nmeaning thereby square deal and\nequal rights for union and non\nunion workers\""
